 the two small FS, which are\nconnected by the (pi, 0) spin-density-wave vector in the parent compound,\nstrongly suggests that the pairing mechanism originates from the inter-band\ninteractions between these two nested FS sheets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jul 2008 18:29:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-07-14"}
