ed stability during the Blazhko cycle. A new\nphenomenological description of the light curve variation is defined that\nseparates the amplitude and phase (period) modulations utilising the phase\ncoherency of the lower order Fourier phases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Jul 2008 11:23:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
